    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1885-07-31T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1885-07-31T00:00:00-05:00" n="219"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d219">
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">No. 219.</seg>
                </opener>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Holguin</persName> and Mr.
                            <persName>Becerra</persName> to Mr. <persName type="to"
                            >Bayard</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">New York</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1885-07-31">
                            <hi rend="italic">July</hi> 31, 1885</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Barranquilla occupied by the Government forces. The port will be opened at once.
                    Prestan taken and tried.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <list>
                            <item>HOLGUIN.</item>
                            <item>BECERRA.</item>
                        </list>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
